Package com.github.epadronu.dwalin.core

Class StrictFacade

java.lang.Object
com.github.epadronu.dwalin.core.StrictFacade
public final class StrictFacade extends Object

A SelenideElement facade for those of us that don't want to expose WebElement instances or WebElement-like behavior in our pages' public API.

See Also:
